    "faq_with_image_m73Xra": {
      "type": "faq-with-image",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_GhRGXt": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How much should you spend on an Engagement Ring?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>There's no strict rule! Traditionally, a guideline of 1–3 months' salary was suggested, but ultimately, the right amount is what feels comfortable and affordable for you.<strong> Focus on finding a ring that your partner will love within your budget.</strong></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_HmVJLJ": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What is the average cost of an Engagement Ring?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>The average cost can vary significantly depending on location, diamond quality, and style. While figures fluctuate, it's more important to focus on your individual budget and preferences rather than a general average.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_xFhTbU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Should I buy a Lab Grown Engagement Ring?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p><strong>Lab-grown diamonds offer the same physical, chemical, and optical properties as natural diamonds</strong> but are created in a controlled environment. They are often a more budget-friendly and sustainable option. The choice is personal and depends on your values and preferences.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_pxHnfz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Does an Engagement Ring come with a box?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Yes, all engagement rings purchased from Griffin & Co come beautifully presented in a complimentary ring box, perfect for proposing and safekeeping.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_BRezAN": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How long should I set aside for my appointment?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>We recommend setting aside about one hour for your consultation. This gives us ample time to discuss your ideas in detail, answer all your questions, and explore different design possibilities without you feeling rushed.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "accordion_GhRGXt",
